Why Code Analysis? 

    - Improves code quality and Maintainability
    - Detects security vulnerabilities early
    - Reduces Technical Debt
    - Helps team follow consistent coding standards
    - Saves time and cost by catching issues before production. 
    - supports automated testing and devops workflow. 

    Top Code analysis Tools
     
     - SonarQube: Popular for continuous inspection of code quality 
     - ESLint: WIdely used for Javascript/TypeScript
     - CheckStyle: Enforces Java Coding standards
     - PMD: Detects common Coding flaws
     - FindBugs/SpotBugs: Finds potential bugs in Java
     - Coverity: Advanced Enterprise level analysis. 

In this course, we will be using SonarQube and CheckStyle. 

